                <author ref="http://syriaca.org/person/10">Aphraates</author>
                <title ref="" type="supplied">The second part of the works of Aphraates; viz. homilies ii-xxii, and the treatise on "the Cluster."</title>
                <finalRubric xml:lang="syr">ܫܠܡ ܠܡܟܬܒ ܒܟܬܒܐ ܗܢܐ ܐܓܪ̈ܬܐ ܟܘܠܗܝܢ . . . ܘܡܪܝ ܝܥܩܘܒ ܚܟܝܡܐ ܦܪܣܝܐ. ܕܗܘܝܢ ܒܡܢܝܢܐ ܥܣܪܝܐ ܘܬܪ̈ܬܝܢ ܥܠ ܐܠܦ ܒܝܬ ܘܚܕܐ ܕܥܠ ܛܘܛܝܬܐ . ܘ . ܘ . ܫܘܒܚܐ ܠܐܒܐ. ܏ܘܫ.
                  <note>The scribe wrote the words <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܕܡܪܝ ܝܥܩܘܒ</foreign> by mistake twice, and then erased them. The letters <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܘܒ</foreign> are still quite distinct.</note><locus from="174a" to="174a"/></finalRubric>
                <colophon><ref target="#p2addition1"/>See additions.</colophon>
